00:24:21,975 --> 00:24:22,856
in the talk as well,

493
00:24:23,997 --> 00:24:26,158
that was a specific person who just like on a lark

494
00:24:27,039 --> 00:24:29,040
made this big list of things I'd like to see

495
00:24:29,080 --> 00:24:30,941
and we read it and we're like, yo, that's awesome.

496
00:24:31,142 --> 00:24:31,682
Let's do that.

