00:24:32,603 --> 00:24:34,504
So we did it, and then at first we said,

498
00:24:35,205 --> 00:24:36,966
when we made the announcement that those were coming in,

499
00:24:37,006 --> 00:24:39,248
we said, hey, this is something that came from the community

500
00:24:39,288 --> 00:24:41,569
and then near the bottom at the end of the wrap up,

501
00:24:41,910 --> 00:24:43,731
we would say, hey, thanks to this person.

502
00:24:43,931 --> 00:24:45,913
So we still find ways to give credit to them,

503
00:24:45,953 --> 00:24:48,034
but the first and foremost thing to do

504
00:24:48,134 --> 00:24:49,535
is to credit the community at large.

505
00:24:50,036 --> 00:24:50,396
Cool, thanks.

506
00:24:51,237 --> 00:24:51,377
Yep.

